CHANGES
=======

1.1.0
-----

* Adds all\_project param. Which allows admins (or users with the right role) to view and edit zones / recordsets for all tenants

1.0.0
-----

* I have simplified the service catalog get
* Tox tests
* Fix oslo.log requirements
* Changelog updated
* Consolidate client methods to utils
* Refactor the module path for suuport future versions. Added recordsets support

0.1.0
-----

* Initial commit. The first prototype version with zone\_list action
